{"tid":2077771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"日食的三年警示 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:57:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3334a3864c8d498a03023b45043cf6e43d41e2","tid":2077771,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200624/20942879/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200624%2F20942879%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=e3f7e7d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200624%2F20942879%2F&h=167ba2d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200624/20942879/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n日食的三年警示 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200624/large/1592895162_328f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200624%2Flarge%2F1592895162_328f.jpg&h=286993be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月香港母親節，商場。。。。。，一片悲憤聲中，過去了。<br />\n<br />\n6月的父親節，妖。。。。。白色恐怖還有暗殺威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n由娃娃抓起的。。。。。的父親，如何過這個節？<br />\n<br />\n最詭異的，是天象。<br />\n<br />\n2020年的父親節。。。。。日食（蝕），實在太巧合。<br />\n<br />\n當月亮走到太陽與。。。。。館海旁觀賞、拍照。<br />\n<br />\n這天象之變，古人視為「天狗食日」，是人世災禍不祥之兆，人們必大聲擊鼓嚇走天狗，以求免災──嚇得走嚇不走，日月也會復原，只是苛政猛於天狗，才發生重大災難來譴責及懲罰，倘君主失德腐敗，上天動怒，意味「亡國更主，近期三月，遠期三年」。<br />\n<br />\n日食形成「上帝的金戒指」，但，會不會是邪魔的鐵鐐銬？我不信，你們信嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}